            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine</strong> and<strong> red pepper</strong> to a tray</p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until everything is cooked through</p>",
